{"tid":635510,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中興指公司進入休克狀態 記者會10分鐘草草結束","createTime":"2018-04-20T07:35:54.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-22T23:59:29.000Z","uid":39464,"like":102,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":62,"replies":[{"pid":"57e23af032cf77277a250189a75875f96218cc14","tid":635510,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-20T07:35:54.000Z","msg":"陷入危機的中興通信（763）約下午三時舉行記者會。據新浪報導，中興通訊董事長殷一民表示，美國的禁令可能導致公司進入休克狀態，對全體員工、遍佈全球的運營商客戶、終端消費者和股東的利益造成直接損害，我們堅決反對。殷一民表示，2017年合規方面投入超5000萬美元。<br />\n<br />\n另外，會上有人透露，在美國做出此決定的一個多月之前，中興首席合規官兼首席法務官被免職。整場記者會為時10分鐘，草草結束。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20180420/58096867\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180420%2F58096867&d=7BieEHDRrS%2FIJH8FDuFIahv1o3X72Fc8dbph17rWX2c%3D&h=1c44e77d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180420%2F58096867&h=f1f17023\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20180420/58096867</a>"},{"pid":"9a6893aaf1b325598cda27b244f58f42a572a89a","tid":635510,"uid":49697,"like":35,"dislike":2,"score":33,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-20T07:38:44.000Z","msg":"抵啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"40aba863742c065bcf6f23715cc5c9adffdc052d","tid":635510,"uid":45518,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-20T07:45:06.000Z","msg":"幾時復牌呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a903392a44fb1943c607ce08b17fbd89145ad5af","tid":635510,"uid":61653,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-20T07:46:55.000Z","msg":"數百萬當做碎銀<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br /